 ],
 "name": "RPlog_The_Prodigal_Son",
 "title": "The Prodigal Son",
 "summary": "Returning to Coral City on Mon Calamari after weeks away researching Mandalore, the antiquarian Paul Nighman crosses paths with the young busker Shenner, newly dressed up and playing for crowds, and the two share a tentative, tender reunion she clearly hopes is more than friendship. Back at the NR barracks, Paul reconnects with his friend Jessalyn Valios -- who confides that Luke Skywalker is leaving for Kashyyyk and that she's been promoted -- while the grief-stricken General Beabous Calhoun (Skeezix) wrestles aloud with a nightmare of his late wife Jenny. When Paul coldly announces he intends to wrap up his goodbyes and avoid getting too attached, Jessalyn slaps him and storms off, leaving Shenner to witness the painful rift. Later, drinking alone in the Briny Deep Tap House, Paul plans an expedition to Kashyyyk with Lando, only for a gang of brutal blue aliens to seize the wounded Jessalyn; Paul, Lando, Skeezix, and the acrobatic child Kian battle them in a bloody brawl, rescuing her at the cost of a savage gash to Paul's neck. His armor of detachment finally shattered, Paul makes his way to his old mentor Dr. Molari Canto, where he at last breaks down and weeps for the first time in his life."
}